OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely dry
OL,6,Fto start Monday evening with late
OL,7,Fsunny spells. Showers developing
OL,8,Fovernight, locally heavy at times and
OL,9,Fperhaps accompanied by hail and
OL,10,Fthunder. A cool night for the time of
OL,11,Fyear, especially under any prolonged
OL,12,Fclear spells.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FA day of sunny spells and
OL,15,Fblustery showers, with the most
OL,16,Ffrequent showers towards the north of
OL,17,Fthe region. Isolated chance of hail
OL,18,Fand thunder. Temperatures a little
OL,19,Fbelow average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
